<title>使用者介面</title>
<p>此頁面解釋 <app>Parabolic</app> 的偏好設定中所有調整使用者介面的選項。</p>

<terms>
    <item>
        <title>主題</title>
        <p>使用者介面主題。</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>預設值：跟隨系統</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Prevent Suspend</title>
        <p>Parabolic will prevent the computer from sleeping while downloads are running.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>預設值：關閉</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>下載歷史記錄長度</title>
        <p>The amount of time to keep past downloads in the app's history.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>預設：一星期</p>
        </note>
    </item>
</terms>
